messages.automaticMessage: Ndee tummbitere firtanaama e jaati e Spanish asliyaare. Nde rewnaaka e neɗɗo tafon. So aɗa yiɗi wallude e ndaartagol, jokkondir e amen nder dobo ɗoo.
messages.originalMessage: Loowdi ndee tummbitere ƴuurii e binndol Spanish ngol asliyaare.
messages.revisedMessage: Ndee tummbitere rewnaama e neɗɗo kadi firtaama e Spanish asliyaare. So nde hasii feewnitaade tafon, jokkondir e amen nder dobo ɗoo.
